#    - Select device: Other (custom name)
#    - Copy the 16-character password
#    - Remove spaces and paste as MAIL_PASSWORD
#
# 3. Example Gmail settings:
#    MAIL_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
#    MAIL_PORT=587
#    MAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls
